<LITERAL>d<REPLACEABLE></REPLACEABLE><REPLACEABLE>n</REPLACEABLE> where <REPLACEABLE>n</REPLACEABLE> is in the range 0&ndash;147 and doesn't end in 8 or 
9 (SCSI RAID)</LITERAL>
</PARA></ENTRY>
</ROW>
<ROW><ENTRY><PARA><LITERAL>s0</LITERAL></PARA></ENTRY>
<ENTRY><PARA>Partition number (slice 
number)</PARA></ENTRY>
<ENTRY><PARA><LITERAL>s0</LITERAL> (root, for the root filesystem)<NEWLINE>
<LITERAL>s1</LITERAL> (swap)<NEWLINE>
